{"id": 158, "genre": 1000, "title": "如何养宠物让你更像一个中产阶级？", "description": "人是铁，范儿是钢，一天不装憋得慌。对于中产阶级这个可爱的群体，我们充满了爱意。生活研究所每周都会推出紧跟时代节奏的“中产阶级装腔指南”，和大家一起分享研究生活的心得。\r\n", "record_count": 2055, "comment_count": 16, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/2016060719463390ulUQrW61bdMotO.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2014-11-24T08:49:56Z", "questions": [{"id": 131, "title": "如何养宠物让你更像一个中产阶级？", "content": "如何养宠物让你更像一个中产阶级？\r\n", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 1110, "content": "绝对注重品种", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193943HAVjGd8Rwr1CWnSo.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 1111, "content": "一般不选择冷僻的物种", "image": "img/option/option/20160607192554WJgCecpowh9M2vQa.jpg", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 1112, "content": "必须给宠物取一个或几个浮夸的名字", "image": "img/option/option/201606071925544wH182hkUaxg3GpI.JPG", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 1113, "content": "对拍摄宠物照片有一种克制的热情", "image": "img/option/option/20160607192554vkJuXzwQdO4pNf3M.jpeg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 1114, "content": "购买各种高级宠物用品即使宠物并不喜欢", "image": "img/option/option/20160607192554vhEr2Lt8Scy9qRVK.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 1115, "content": "转发领养信息但自己并不领养", "image": "img/option/option/20160607192554hNDap2e3PIcZwMT8.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 1116, "content": "不亲自给宠物洗澡", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193959uxYFVPL0jDgzTCvt.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}